    Page: 456
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Suffering
---
The more you move towards the goal, all sorrow will cease. Even if there is
sorrow, you will become impervious to it. It will not touch you. There will
be an inner strength created within you where even sorrow will not have a
meaning for you. You will smile even at misfortune and suffering.
